principals that we had at the company, who just thought it would be like a really uniting theme.

00:15:55.799 --> 00:16:03.000
And then we pitched it to the executives that we knew were already on board and going to help us.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:09.159
And they were like, yeah, absolutely. Let's go forward with it. And we thought that it was the

00:16:09.159 --> 00:16:18.520
