powerful tool, which is using analogies to chemical manufacturing. So everybody in R&D knows

00:23:02.760 --> 00:23:07.640
you make a little flask of your chemical on the lab. You're like, yeah, I got a new product,

00:23:08.119 --> 00:23:17.160
