00:23:56.040 --> 00:24:02.359
have this. And so that's been the most powerful thing. I've heard a lot of feedback about

00:24:04.439 --> 00:24:13.400
just putting the tasks that a deployment and development team has to do into the words of

00:24:14.280 --> 00:24:19.880
your client, right? And so I'm trying to get that documented, get that in an easily digestible form

00:24:19.880 --> 00:24:27.400
